{{#partial "content"}}
    <h1>Cheery Greetings!</h1>
    <p>Hello from afar...</p>
    <p>Dear {{ recipient }},</p>
    <p>How are you? I hope that you are having a nice weekend. I'm vacationing in the Iceland while I learn programming!</p>
    <p>{{ recipient }}, you would not believe how cold it is here. I should have gone to Hawaii indtead.</p>
    <p>But I like programming a lot, so I've got that going for me.</p>
    <p>Looking forward to seeing you soon. I'll bring you back a souvenir</p>
    <p>Cheers, </p>
    <p>Travel Enthusiast, {{ sender }}</p>
{{/partial}}
